{"tid":2066760,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連登仔一齊係到發誓，只會選本土","createTime":"2020-06-16T13:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T00:48:04.000Z","uid":42149,"like":74,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1b91b7f768adfb9dabcf2b823f0471b8fa8b84","tid":2066760,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"而家見到好多本土新人都因為泛民等有強大既財力而逼到退選。<br />\n但我地唔係要泛民個套，我地要本土，我地要有新血入議會。<br />\n<br />\n所以懇請各位係呢到發誓，無論點都好。<br />\n我投票既首選係本土&gt; 泛民<br />\n<br />\n亦同時希望更多本土人士出黎選，唔好怕。<br />\n香港去到今時今日，已經冇野好驚！<br />\n<br />\n我係到發誓，黎緊立法會選舉，有本土投本土，冇本土先投泛民。<br />\n如有違世，死全家<br />\n<br />\n利申：熱狗唔係本土<br />\n<br />\n當議會大多數都係本土新血，泛民冇任何理由唔協助佢地。<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立。唯一出路"},{"pid":"ef99f29d96944ebb32b0cf2aee4c343771823fb2","tid":2066760,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"推 一齊發誓"},{"pid":"ed91e0db42e867183887ebc443a67ef32239cee7","tid":2066760,"uid":133333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"你估下飯民會唔會協助佢哋"},{"pid":"b87ea6ac311a4bdb1e306e33cf4b589cd5320680","tid":2066760,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"3f37b6afa88370dad265bc10bbaf3b96f2103bd5","tid":2066760,"uid":42149,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ed91e0db42e867183887ebc443a67ef32239cee7","tid":2066760,"uid":133333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"你估下飯民會唔會協助佢哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"最少我地成功推左堆本土入去先。<br />\n好過好似而家咁。<br />\n議會要新血"},{"pid":"140be1e9d1ae398837478871058d7c0fe713b208","tid":2066760,"uid":13000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"啱呀，有本土投本土"},{"pid":"3fff58ff72c6f0f72ce2ce04a256e67ed030b6fa","tid":2066760,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:26:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f028a2477fa5ac33cd1dc6427c8591aeac2b9985","tid":2066760,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"傻閪又選d忽然本土既廢柴入去 佢地柒到冇埋個議席之後又係度嘈😂香港政治專選廢柴😂"},{"pid":"bd4c7c17d52d6398c1c9d2cbc29e679186e3d44c","tid":2066760,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:28:57.000Z","msg":"乜水係本土又會選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇過"},{"pid":"0ce763ed7dc3974060fdc04ad90c7ba7b9a60aae","tid":2066760,"uid":168400,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31e009a540526810a4721904e45b148cdb64f77e","tid":2066760,"uid":42149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f028a2477fa5ac33cd1dc6427c8591aeac2b9985","tid":2066760,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"傻閪又選d忽然本土既廢柴入去 佢地柒到冇埋個議席之後又係度嘈😂香港政治專選廢柴😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"選泛民入去唔係問題，但泛民好多都鳩流流根本係打份工。<br />\n黃碧雲；葉建源；梁耀忠入去做咩。<br />\n<br />\n呢一年好多人都醒左，點解唔可以比個機會佢地入去？永續一批坐左係到咁多年但冇咩成效既人入去就有用？<br />\n<br />\n呢一年唔係因為出面打到仆街，死既死，流亡既流亡，仲行以前個套有用咩？<br />\n<br />\n新一批泛民係進化左，進化得最快個個係勇武峯，但其他都仲係進化得未夠快。<br />\n<br />\n一係就泛民自己同本土協調好，唔好拎盡哂所有位。<br />\n<br />\n但我都會有本土投本土，冇本土先投泛民"},{"pid":"5b022459c8ebf151e852ced995d57b9fdf7f28b7","tid":2066760,"uid":260181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:00:33.000Z","msg":"唔會投販民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2f5c6d7857b3c9dbd6d8d59ce58aa5be4020b2","tid":2066760,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b022459c8ebf151e852ced995d57b9fdf7f28b7","tid":2066760,"uid":260181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"